$$m^2+y^2 \geq \left( 2y-1 \right)^2 \Leftrightarrow \dfrac{2-\sqrt{1+3m^2}}{3} \leq y \leq \dfrac{2+\sqrt{1+3m^2}}{3}. $$ 
